    <description>Runs on updates to the School Object, specifically at the Premium ECE update, but can be expanded in the future
6/26/24 - BW - Adding logic to populate Billing Activation Start Date
10/02/24 - PE - Updated entry criteria so that flow will also fire if &quot;Verification Pending Date&quot; is updated.
02/13/25 - BW - Adding logic to populate Date of Multisite Removal based off of Number of Sites on SO
04/16/25 - JS - Adding logic to populate BNP Graduation Date on related Account and CF when SaaS Adding Students Stage is updated
05/29/25 - PE - Add logic to differentiate how we populate BASD for SaaS and Gov
6/16/25- JH: updated so that this will also be triggered for when the &quot;Bill Rate Uploaded Date&quot; is populated on the school object so that it syncs to the account record.</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <name>forPremiumNonActiveReason</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF(AND(TEXT({!$Record.Brightwheel_Plan__c})&lt;&gt;TEXT({!$Record__Prior.Brightwheel_Plan__c}), ISPICKVAL({!$Record__Prior.Brightwheel_Plan__c},&apos;Premium&apos;)),
&apos;Brightwheel Plan updated&apos;,

IF({!$Record.Program_type__c}&lt;&gt;{!$Record__Prior.Program_type__c},
&apos;Center Type updated&apos;,

IF({!$Record.State__c}&lt;&gt;{!$Record__Prior.State__c},
&apos;Location updated&apos;,&apos;&apos;)))</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>IsNew</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IsNew()</expression>
    </formulas>
